{
  "chapter": 4,
  "chapter_summary": "向衡飞潜入锦室，目睹玉面狐张先辽趁海萍被迷药放倒之际肆意侵犯，怒而出声。张先辽发现向衡飞后不以为意，出言讥讽并动腿攻击，却被向衡飞轻松制服。两人追至城内荒地交手，向衡飞以空灵步法戏耍张先辽，又以两指夹住缅刀，令其颜面尽失。向衡飞夺取红旗帮传令令牌，赶往破庙欲救王一萍，却发现王一萍与贺衔山已趁乱逃脱，地上留下\"明夜三更，原地相会\"的砖刻字迹。次日子夜，王一萍与贺衔山在王家后花园等候向衡飞，阴山四煞中的端木华与公孙剑突然现身，声称已投靠红旗帮为四大护法，要向贺衔山讨还旧债。与此同时，向衡飞赴约途中在密林遭玉面狐张先辽与阴山四煞老大独孤虹、老三上官云截击。上官云施展勾魂十二抓，向衡飞以空灵步法尽数避开；独孤虹与上官云又以钢拐合击之术围攻，向衡飞情势危急之际，红旗帮发出绿色信号弹，独孤虹等人撤走。向衡飞赶至王家花园，发现浓烟冲天，王宅已陷入火海。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不要脸的贱女人！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我说北京城里是谁有这份胆量，竟敢管张大爷的闲事？嘿！嘿，想不到原来是大名鼎鼎的受气包。嘿！嘿！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你还有胆站在这里？还不给你张大爷滚下去。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呀",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "滚下去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "院里众人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "捉贼呀！捉贼呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "受气包，瞧不出你倒还有两下子。走，咱们找个清静地方，大爷倒要跟你好好比划比划。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "打手",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好哇，受气包，你真有出息，偷鸡摸狗上房子，你可全学会啦！",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "舵主不是说有意跟我比划比划？走啊！我向衡飞能有机会跟舵主过招，真是三生有幸！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张舵主，我看这片空地已足够咱们活动，不知舵主意下如何？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "也好，就待本舵主在此地收拾你便了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张舵主，我看你还是省点力气吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我要你立即释放王公子！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王公子与红旗帮素无过节，我们不会为难他。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "事不宜迟，要救人咱们这就去吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "些许小事，也不敢劳动舵主大驾。但请借贵帮传令信牌一用即可。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是舵主不愿借用？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "区区一块信牌，借用一次，又有何妨？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "拿去！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "有劳舵主在此稍候，等我放出王公子之后，再来放你。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_tong_luo",
      "speaker_name": "小铜锣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "诸位听着，想我小铜锣冒险将这姓贺的弄回来，目的不在为个人立功，全在为帮中除害。是功是过，自有舵主定夺，如今为防意外，最好先将他脚筋挑断……",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "住手，我有话说！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮众",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "妈的，还挨个什么劲，揍啊！使劲揍！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮徒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "敢问尊驾手持本帮令牌，不知有何吩咐？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "奉贵帮张舵主之命，将王公子立即释出，不得有任何延误。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "红旗帮徒",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王公子和那姓贺的都不见啦！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他该不会爽约不来吧！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 366,
      "line_end": 366
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贺兄，你认为姓向的会来吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 372
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除非他——",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下已在此守候多时了，尊驾既已来到墙外，何不进园一叙？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 388,
      "line_end": 388
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阴山四煞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个不知天高地厚的小娃娃，凭你这么点微末道行，也敢向咱们红旗帮伸手。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 394,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不知江湖中令人景仰不已的阴山四煞，是何时跟红旗帮套上了交情？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "阴山四煞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓贺的，老实告诉你，昔年的阴山四煞，今天已成为红旗帮的四大护法。素闻尊驾自恃绝艺在身，目中无人，我们这群老不死的今夜第一次伸手替红旗帮管事，说不得要向尊驾讨还一些公道。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 406
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下王一萍，与诸位素昧平生。诸位深夜逾墙而入，来意显属不善，在下倒要请教。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 418
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_he_xian_shan",
      "speaker_name": "贺衔山",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "王兄，这几人全冲着我一人而来，回头如果动手，王兄尽管一旁静观。万一小弟不幸失手丧命，尚祈王兄念在相交一场，设法遣人将小弟尸体运回桐庐，小弟在九泉之下，亦感激万分！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贺兄放心，贺兄如此说法，岂不将王某看得一钱不值？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 432,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_duan_mu_hua",
      "speaker_name": "端木华",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们阴山四煞行事素来有个规矩，如果对方知趣，我阴山四煞念在彼此同属武林一脉，让他死个痛快，如果不自量力，要想拒抗，哼！哼！到时可别怨我阴山四煞下手狠毒。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_yi_ping",
      "speaker_name": "王一萍",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贺兄在此是客，有什么事我这个做主人的总该算上一份。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓向的，你这会才来呀，等得你大爷好苦！",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 480,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦！原来是张舵主。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓向的小子听着，在你眼前站着的是当今武林中威名远播的阴山四煞，你小子微末伎俩，趁早束手就擒。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 504
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_yun",
      "speaker_name": "上官云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "张舵主，你收拾不了他，还是让我来打发他。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 526,
      "line_end": 526
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "久闻阴山四煞武功别具一格，早就想领教领教。可惜我今夜与人另有约会，无法在此奉陪。诸位有何指教，请另约时地，到时我决不爽约。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 532,
      "line_end": 532
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_yun",
      "speaker_name": "上官云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，你瞧瞧，这小子倒还真狂得可以，你说该怎么收拾他？",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 538,
      "line_end": 538
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_hong",
      "speaker_name": "独孤虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "越干脆越好，听说贺衔山那小子手下不弱，有老二他们两个人前去，自是胜券在握，怕只怕那家伙脚底抹油，咱们另有要事，无法穷追！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 540,
      "line_end": 540
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhang_xian_liao",
      "speaker_name": "张先辽",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姓向的，你乖乖地将昨晚偷走的令牌双手奉回，跪在两位护法面前请求宽恕，也许还可落个痛快！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 550,
      "line_end": 550
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还你就还你，接着。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 554,
      "line_end": 554
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_yun",
      "speaker_name": "上官云",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子，看你不出还有点门道，我上官云自不量力，想要向阁下讨教几招！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_hong",
      "speaker_name": "独孤虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "记得昔年名震宇内的威震河朔魏灵飞，勉强躲过我的勾魂十二抓，所施身法与你此刻所施大同小异，敢问你与北灵如何称呼？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 622,
      "line_end": 622
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_heng_fei",
      "speaker_name": "向衡飞",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我可不知道什么南灵北灵，要打请赶快动手，不然，我可要去赴友人之约了。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 624,
      "line_end": 624
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_du_gu_hong",
      "speaker_name": "独孤虹",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哼，今夜之战，到此为止。明年今日，独孤虹在阴山恭候大驾。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 4,
      "line_start": 658,
      "line_end": 658
    }
  ],
